0tariffs%20raise%20prices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20of%20Europe's%20biggest%20airline%20is%20in%20a%20growing%20spat%20with%20a%20US%20congressman%20who%20warned%20him%20against%20buying%20any%20planes%20from%20China%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairlines-trump-tariff-turbulence-delta-united-american-hopes-bumper-2025-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariffs%20cause%20uncertainty%20in%20the%20aviation%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20media%20outlets%20reported%20Thursday%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fryanair-ceo-says-boeing-lack-attention-detail-plane-production-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERyanair's%20Michael%20O'Leary%3C%2Fa%3E%20threatened%20to%20cancel%20orders%20for%20new%20planes%20from%20Boeing%20if%20tariffs%20are%20levied%20on%20the%20jets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20came%20two%20days%20after%20he%20was%20sent%20a%20letter%20by%20Raja%20Krishnamoorthi%2C%20the%20ranking%20member%20of%20the%20House%20Select%20Committee%20on%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20was%20raising%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20concerns%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fryanair-flight-review-first-time-bag-fees-charges-wasnt-convinced-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERyanair%3C%2Fa%3E%20boss's%20comments%20in%20a%20March%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Chinese%20are%20basically%20building%20a%20fucking%20A320.%20So%20if%20it%20was%20cheap%20enough%20%E2%80%94%2010%20or%2020%25%20cheaper%20than%20an%20Airbus%20aircraft%20%E2%80%94%20then%20we'd%20order%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Leary%20told%20travel%20industry%20outlet%20Skift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcomac-c919-chinese-commercial-jet-built-rival-boeing-and-airbus-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EComac%20C919%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20narrow-body%20plane%20similar%20to%20the%20best-selling%20Airbus%20A320%20and%20Boeing's%20737.%20It%20has%20received%20over%201%2C000%20orders%2C%20almost%20entirely%20from%20Chinese%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirbus%20CEO%20Guillaume%20Faury%20believes%20Comac's%20rise%20could%20see%20the%20sector%20go%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20a%20duopoly%20to%20a%20potential%20triopoly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERyanair%20is%20a%20budget%20carrier%20with%20hundreds%20of%20Boeing%20737s%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20American%20planemaker's%20biggest%20customers.%20It%20also%20operates%20smaller%20subsidiaries%20that%20fly%20Airbus%20jets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ryanair%20has%20kept%20its%20options%20open%20over%20concerns%20the%20European%20Union%20could%20impose%20tariffs%20on%20American%20products%20in%20response%20to%20Donald%20Trump's%2010%25%20levy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKrishnamoorthi%2C%20the%20Democratic%20representative%20for%20Illinois's%208th%20congressional%20district%2C%20told%20the%20Irish%20airline%20it%20shouldn't%20do%20business%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20cited%20a%20Justice%20Department%20indictment%20from%202018%20that%20accused%2010%20Chinese%20intelligence%20operatives%20of%20participating%20in%20a%20corporate%20espionage%20campaign%20to%20steal%20information%20about%20turbofan%20jet%20engines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20%26quot%3Bevidence%20indicates%26quot%3B%20Comac%20has%20received%20government%20subsidies%2C%C2%A0although%20Boeing%20and%20Airbus%20have%20also%20done%20so%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ryanair%20boss%20appears%20to%20be%20holding%20firm%2C%20reportedly%20saying%20in%20his%20Thursday%20reply%20that%20he%20would%20look%20to%20alternative%20suppliers%2C%20including%20Comac.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERyanair%20and%20the%20Democrats%20of%20the%20House%20Select%20Committee%20on%20the%20CCP%20did%20not%20reply%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20sent%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Comac%20would%20massively%20benefit%20f