-menstrual-hygiene-green-pencil-foundation-climate-change%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealth%20and%20safety%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20top%20priorities.%20And%20with%20this%2C%20I%20can%20sleep%20easily.%20I%20have%20even%20recommended%20it%20to%20nearby%20showroom%20owners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20few%20have%20already%20picked%20it%20up%20after%20seeing%20it%20in%20action%20here%2C%20others%20keep%20dropping%20by%20to%20get%20their%20batteries%20tested%20at%20our%20place.%20It%20is%20slowly%20becoming%20a%20standard%2C%20and%20that%20is%20a%20good%20thing%20for%20all%20of%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHigh-tech%20without%20the%20high%20price%20tag%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20priced%20at%20Rs%2025%2C000%2C%20the%20device%20is%20now%20available%20to%20garages%20and%20smaller%20service%20centres%20for%20as%20little%20as%20Rs%2010%2C000%2C%20due%20to%20a%20redesigned%20business%20model%20focused%20on%20accessibility.%20The%20kit%20includes%20the%20EV%20Doctor%20device%2C%20power%20supply%2C%20extra%20connectors%2C%20a%20detailed%20user%20manual%2C%20two%20years%20of%20warranty%2C%20and%20lifetime%20upgrades%2C%20all%20aimed%20at%20democratising%20battery%20diagnostics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20sets%20the%20device%20apart%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20its%20speed%3B%20it%20is%20also%20the%20science%20behind%20its%20safety.%20Working%20with%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20Gandhinagar%20(IIT-GN)%2C%20the%20team%20conducted%20over%2060%20thermal%20runaway%20tests%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20device%20can%20reliably%20detect%20potential%20fire%20hazards%20in%20battery%20cells.%20These%20tests%20also%20informed%20the%20device%E2%80%99s%20safety%20prediction%20algorithms%2C%20which%20continue%20to%20evolve%20with%20every%20battery%20scanned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20consciously%20reduced%20the%20size%20from%201%20kilogram%20to%20300%20grams%20to%20make%20it%20portable%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ajay%20says.%