-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T220922.780_11zon-1746031177-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T220922.780_11zon-1746031177-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T220922.780_11zon-1746031177-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-424419%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShubham%20conducts%20demonstrations%20of%20the%20EV%20Doctor%20for%20dealers%20so%20they%20know%20the%20benefits%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20major%20priority%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20was%20thermal%20runaway%2C%20the%20phenomenon%20where%20a%20battery%20overheats%20and%20potentially%20catches%20fire.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20EV%20Doctor%20team%20had%20done%20extensive%20testing%20in%20this%20area%2C%20which%20allowed%20us%20to%20train%20the%20AI%20models%20with%20real-world%20data.%20It%20gave%20the%20device%20a%20strong%20edge%20over%20other%20solutions%20in%20terms%20of%20risk%20prediction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20success%2C%20the%20co-founders%20consider%20EV%20Doctor%20just%20the%20beginning.%20Their%20next%20project%2C%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20Energy%20AI%20Labs%2C%20is%20to%20build%20a%20universal%20operating%20system%20for%20batteries%2C%20essentially%20giving%20%E2%80%98a%20brain%20to%20every%20battery%20on%20Earth.%E2%80%99%20This%20platform%20will%20allow%20continuous%20diagnostics%2C%20live%20updates%2C%20and%20predictive%20insights%20that%20can%20one%20day%20power%20everything%20from%20electric%20scooters%20to%20grid-scale%20storage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Proper%20testing%20can%20extend%20a%20battery%E2%80%99s%20life%20by%20eight%20to%2010%20years%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20moving%20towards%20a%20future%20where%20batteries%20will%20not%20just%20store%20energy%2C%20but%20make%20intelligent%20decisions%20about%20how%20they%20are%20used%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shubham.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%20want%20to%20be%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20that%20innovation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20agrees%20and%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20biggest%20problem%20in%20the%20EV%20industry%20is%20not%20the%20battery.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20lack%20of%20reliable%20information%20about%20it%20and%20the%20rudimentary%20methods%20that%20people%20keep%20using%20to%20check%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20component.%20We%20are%20changing%20that%20by%20bringing%20truth%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263986%2Fbengaluru-startup-charge-electric-vehicle-fast-battery-pack-charging-station%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etransparency%20into%20battery%20performance%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20chance%20observation%20in%20a%20workshop%20to%20building%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20impactful%20battery%20diagnostics%20tools%2C%20the%20co-founders%20have%20been%20successful%20in%20creating%20their%20name%20in%20this%20sector.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20batteries%20are%20tested%20properly%2C%20their%20lifespan%20can%20be%20extended%20by%20eight%20to%2010%20years%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20what%20our%20device%20is%20helping%20to%20achieve.%20Now%2C%20more%20people%20can%20shift%20to%20this%20mode%20of%20transportation%20without%20worrying%20about%20potential%20hazards%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Vidya%20Gowri%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%20Shubham%20Mishra%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746156624000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FShubham-Mishra-speaking-at-IIT-B-1-1746029462.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D424375%22%2C%22